  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Finance Manager (Full Sets)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a local leading player in F&B Distribution industry. They are now recruiting a Finance Manager to be part of their Finance team to assist the next phase of their business. They are located in the East Area.</strong></p><p>Roles and Responsibilities of Finance Manager:</p><ul><li>Handle full-set accounts, month-end/year-end closings, and reconciliations.</li><li>Prepare financial statements and management reports.</li><li>Lead and supervise one finance staff.</li><li>Develop budgets, forecasts, and cash flow projections.</li><li>Perform financial analysis to identify trends, risks, and opportunities.</li><li>Ensure compliance with accounting standards, tax, and audit requirements.</li><li>Improve finance processes and reporting efficiency.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Accountancy, Finance, or related discipline.</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Dynamics or SAP system.</li><li>Minimum 5 to 8 years of experience in handling full set of accounts.</li><li>Singaporean only.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</li><li>EA License No. 19C9682</li><li>EA Reg. No. R22108850 (Chan Mun Mun)</li></ul>",
